{"id": "ChIJDwXFbSlL3YAR6ipesSM96e8", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 13582, "displayName": {"text": "Del Amo Fashion Center", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Large mall offers trendy retailers, restaurants & a theater, plus a garden-inspired dining pavilion.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJDwXFbSlL3YAR6ipesSM96e8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paSFpDMXRYelE1TVdRMVprWlJialppZWtwcVUxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Visiting Del Amo Fashion Center in Torrance was a surprisingly fun and enjoyable experience! This is one of the larger shopping destinations in Southern California with a huge variety of stores and plenty to explore — from fashion retailers to specialty shops. Many visitors note there are over 250 stores to browse, including major anchors like Macy’s and Nordstrom, as well as a diverse mix of national brands and unique shops.  ￼\n\nOne of the highlights is the abundant dining options, including a dedicated food court area like Patio Cafes food court plus sit-down restaurants and café choices. Whether you’re looking for a quick snack or a full meal, there’s something for families and groups.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Visiting Del Amo Fashion Center in Torrance was a surprisingly fun and enjoyable experience! This is one of the larger shopping destinations in Southern California with a huge variety of stores and plenty to explore — from fashion retailers to specialty shops. Many visitors note there are over 250 stores to browse, including major anchors like Macy’s and Nordstrom, as well as a diverse mix of national brands and unique shops.  ￼\n\nOne of the highlights is the abundant dining options, including a dedicated food court area like Patio Cafes food court plus sit-down restaurants and café choices. Whether you’re looking for a quick snack or a full meal, there’s something for families and groups.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Gigi Wes Travels", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113435890238270402639/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvXW7dd0Ac_xflkG_aFMFz6PNByMdcLAu59C7KdhaMRPqgzUQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-24T00:31:14.970489842Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paSFpDMXRYelE1TVdRMVprWlJialppZWtwcVUxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paSFpDMXRYelE1TVdRMVprWlJialppZWtwcVUxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd4b296dc5050f:0xefe93d23b15e2aea"}, {"name": "places/ChIJDwXFbSlL3YAR6ipesSM96e8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5RFNGZHNhV0p1VGxGcWNFeGxOall3Y1dwWlFVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "10 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Del Amo Fashion Center is amazing! It’s a huge mall with all types of stores and so many restaurants. It’s the perfect place to walk, shop, and grab a bite — whether you’re alone or with family. The mall is safe, beautiful, and just a great everyday spot for all your needs.\n\nI recently went with my husband, and we spent about 4 hours walking around, eating, and shopping. What a fantastic experience! I absolutely love this mall and highly recommend it. I’ll always go back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Del Amo Fashion Center is amazing! It’s a huge mall with all types of stores and so many restaurants. It’s the perfect place to walk, shop, and grab a bite — whether you’re alone or with family. The mall is safe, beautiful, and just a great everyday spot for all your needs.\n\nI recently went with my husband, and we spent about 4 hours walking around, eating, and shopping. What a fantastic experience! I absolutely love this mall and highly recommend it. I’ll always go back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mariana Moraes", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112619468969470507855/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzMwxMU6_L4PdSLH-FyDZwKuM007fSXmYYfPz3FOKEpOloxXg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-08-18T17:56:09.876650034Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5RFNGZHNhV0p1VGxGcWNFeGxOall3Y1dwWlFVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5RFNGZHNhV0p1VGxGcWNFeGxOall3Y1dwWlFVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd4b296dc5050f:0xefe93d23b15e2aea"}, {"name": "places/ChIJDwXFbSlL3YAR6ipesSM96e8/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNnaExHSG5BRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Del Amo Fashion Center is one of the best shopping destinations in Southern California. With a perfect blend of high-end retailers, popular brands, and unique local shops, it offers something for everyone. The mall is spacious, clean, and well-designed, making for a comfortable shopping experience.\n\nBeyond shopping, Del Amo has a fantastic selection of dining options, from casual bites to upscale restaurants. Whether you’re grabbing a quick coffee or sitting down for a meal, there’s plenty of variety. The outdoor areas and modern architecture add to the upscale feel, making it a great place to spend an afternoon.\n\nParking is generally easy, with plenty of spaces and valet options. The mall also hosts seasonal events, making it more than just a shopping center—it’s a true community hub. If you’re in the area, Del Amo Fashion Center is definitely worth a visit!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Del Amo Fashion Center is one of the best shopping destinations in Southern California. With a perfect blend of high-end retailers, popular brands, and unique local shops, it offers something for everyone. The mall is spacious, clean, and well-designed, making for a comfortable shopping experience.\n\nBeyond shopping, Del Amo has a fantastic selection of dining options, from casual bites to upscale restaurants. Whether you’re grabbing a quick coffee or sitting down for a meal, there’s plenty of variety. The outdoor areas and modern architecture add to the upscale feel, making it a great place to spend an afternoon.\n\nParking is generally easy, with plenty of spaces and valet options. The mall also hosts seasonal events, making it more than just a shopping center—it’s a true community hub. If you’re in the area, Del Amo Fashion Center is definitely worth a visit!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Derek Eckley", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117315934959202166637/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLh806nnbkZ3YGAaztA16kKf-ft-REI3t1oKe-iY8oeoyqnAw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-02-14T05:15:34.201829Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNnaExHSG5BRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNnaExHSG5BRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd4b296dc5050f:0xefe93d23b15e2aea"}, {"name": "places/ChIJDwXFbSlL3YAR6ipesSM96e8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25adVZWOHhSVUZOWW1KVWJtSm5VblZ1VHpSQ2VrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is a wonderful mall. There are numerous high-end restaurants, clothing, stores, and bases in Nordstrom's. There are places to sit and relax with a cup of coffee and a fabulous bakery. Del Amo fashion center has only improved over the years", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is a wonderful mall. There are numerous high-end restaurants, clothing, stores, and bases in Nordstrom's. There are places to sit and relax with a cup of coffee and a fabulous bakery. Del Amo fashion center has only improved over the years", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName":